            <div class="instructions">
                <h3>How It Works</h3>
                <p>The solution uses a JavaScript array to track visited tabs. When a tab is selected, the system checks if it has been visited before.</p>
                <p>If it has, an alert is shown. The code uses EasyUI's <span class="highlight">onSelect</span> event handler to implement this functionality.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>EasyUI Tab Alert Implementation | Â© 2023 Bank Portal</p>
        </div>
